\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sacrud/ps_tree\">ps_tree</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sacrud/ps_tree\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2,\"repo\":\"sacrud/ps_tree\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - extension for\n<a href=\"https://github.com/sacrud/pyramid_sacrud\">pyramid_sacrud</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sacrud/pyramid_sacrud\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">50</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":50,\"repo\":\"sacrud/pyramid_sacrud\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> which displays\na list of records as tree. This works fine with models from\n<a href=\"https://github.com/uralbash/sqlalchemy_mptt\">sqlalchemy_mptt</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/uralbash/sqlalchemy_mptt\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">169</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":169,\"repo\":\"uralbash/sqlalchemy_mptt\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-02-07T10:53:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rust-unofficial/awesome-rust","categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Encoding</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>RON (Rusty Object Notation)\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ron-rs/ron\">https://github.com/ron-rs/ron</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ron-rs/ron\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.5k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1540,\"repo\":\"ron-rs/ron\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> — <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/https://github.com/ron-rs/ron\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/ron-rs/ron.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-02-07T10:47:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"fffaraz/awesome-cpp","categoryHTML":"<h2>Concurrency</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/concurrencykit/ck\">ck</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/concurrencykit/ck\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight